public record MessageBody(String content, Instant timestamp, long salt, LastSeenMessageList lastSeenMessages) extends Record
A body of a message, including the content, timestamp, salt used for the digest (the hashed body), and the list of players' "last seen messages". Other bits of information, such as sender, are included directly in the packet.
